trans-unit.source: Provides information about a type that components can access across application domain and process boundaries.
trans-unit.target: Fornece informações sobre um tipo que podem acessar componentes nos limites de domínio e o processo do aplicativo.

trans-unit.source: The RemoteTypeData structure provides information about an object that implements the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: A estrutura RemoteTypeData fornece informações sobre um objeto que implementa o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>interface.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>

trans-unit.source: To get type information about a remote object, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A> method to obtain an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter informações sobre um objeto remoto de tipo, componentes de chamar o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>método para obter um <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Then, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A> method to get a RemoteTypeData.
trans-unit.target: Em seguida, chamada de componentes de <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>método para obter um RemoteTypeData.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Indicates the rank (that is, the number of dimensions) of the remote array type that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Indica a classificação (ou seja, o número de dimensões) da matriz remota de tipo que este <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"> </xref> descreve.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData> describes an array, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> field.
trans-unit.target: Para determinar se um <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>descreve uma matriz, use o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray>campo.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>

trans-unit.source: The assembly-qualified name of a type includes the name of the assembly from which the type was loaded.
trans-unit.target: O nome qualificado do assembly de um tipo inclui o nome do assembly do qual o tipo foi carregado.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the format of an assembly-qualified name, see the <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o formato de um nome qualificado de assembly, consulte o <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade.</xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
